Interface RequirementTraceLinkIfc

  • All Superinterfaces:
    _RequirementTraceLinkIfc, _TraceLinkIfc, BinaryLink, TraceLinkIfc
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    _RequirementO2OTraceLink, _RequirementV2VTraceLink, RequirementO2OTraceLink, RequirementV2VTraceLink

    @GenAsBinaryLink(interfaces=TraceLinkIfc.class,
                 roleA=@GeneratedRole(name="traceable",type=Traceable.class,supportedAPI=PUBLIC,cardinality=ONE),
                 roleB=@GeneratedRole(name="tracedTo",type=RequirementItemIfc.class,supportedAPI=PUBLIC,cardinality=ONE))
public interface RequirementTraceLinkIfc
extends _RequirementTraceLinkIfc
    This is tagging interface for all requirement related trace links. All requirement related trace links must implement this interface to distinguish the trace link at requirement module level.

    Supported API: true

    Extendable: false
